archivedate=August 19, 2007}}\n* {{Structurae|id=20000262|title=San Francisco\u2013Oakland Bay Bridge (West Span)}}\n* {{Structurae|id=20000564|title=San Francisco\u2013Oakland Bay Bridge (Old East Span)}}\n* {{Structurae|id=20000914|title=San Francisco\u2013Oakland Bay Bridge (New East Span)}}\n* {{HAER |survey=CA-32 |id=ca1352 |title=San Francisco Oakland Bay Bridge |photos=415 |dwgs=20 |data=273 |cap=48}}\n* {{HAER |survey=CA-230 |id=ca2555 |title=San Francisco Oakland Bay Bridge Firehouse |photos=1 |data=2 |cap=1 |link=no}}\n* [http://www.batolls.info/bridges/san_francisco_oakland_bay_bridge.html Live Toll Prices for San Francisco\u2013Oakland Bay Bridge]\n\n{{Crossings navbox\n| structure = Crossings\n| place = [[San Francisco Bay]]\n| bridge = San Francisco\u2013Oakland Bay Bridge\n| bridge signs = [[File:I-80 (CA).svg|20px|Interstate 80]]\n| upstream text = South\n| upstream = [[San Mateo\u2013Hayward Bridge]]\n| upstream signs = [[File:California 92.svg|20px|State Route 92]]\n| downstream text = North\n| downstream = [[Transbay Tube]]\n| downstream signs = [[File:Bart-logo.svg|20px|BART]]\n| note = The [[Transbay Tube]] crosses the San Francisco\u2013Oakland Bay Bridge, so it is both north and south of the San Francisco\u2013Oakland Bay Bridge.\n}}\n{{San Francisco attractions}}\n{{National Register of Historic Places}}\n{{Oakland, California}}\n{{San Francisco Bay watershed}}\n{{Bay Area tunnels}}\n<!--{{fixbunching|end}}-->\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:San Francisco-Oakland Bay Bridge}}\n[[Category:Bridge disasters in the United States]]\n[[Category:Bridge disasters caused by earthquakes]]\n[[Category:Bridges completed in 1936]]\n[[Category:Bridges in the San Francisco Bay Area]]\n[[Category:Bridges on the Interstate Highway System]]\n[[Category:Road bridges on the National Register of Historic Places in California]]\n[[Category:Buildings and structures in Oakland, California]]\n[[Category:Cantilever bridges]]\n[[Category:Double-decker bridges]]\n[[Category:Historic A