tions|work=Gadget360|language=en}}</ref><ref name=\"Camera\">{{Cite news|url=https://www.gsmarena.com/redmi_note_8_pro_is_officially_the_first_smartphone_with_a_64_mp_camera-news-38926.php|title=Redmi Note 8 Pro is officially the first smartphone with a 64 MP camera|work=GSMArena|language=en}}</ref> The Redmi Note 8 Pro is the first smartphone released with a 64 megapixel camera.<ref name=\"Camera\"/> The Note 8 Pro was released in Italy on 23 September 2019.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hynerd.it/tech/redmi-note-8-pro-approda-ufficialmente-in-italia/|title=Redmi Note 8 Pro approda ufficialmente in italia!|language=it}}</ref>\n\n== Specifications ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Variants !! Redmi Note 8 !! Redmi Note 8T !! Redmi Note 8 Pro\n|-\n! Processor\n| Qualcomm Snapdragon 665 AIE || Qualcomm Snapdragon 665 AIE || MediaTek Helio G90T\n|-\n! Rear Camera\n| 48MP || 48MP || 64MP\n|-\n! Ultra Wide Angle Camera\n| 8MP || 8MP || 8MP\n|-\n! Depth Sensor Camera\n| 2MP || 2MP || 2MP\n|-\n! Macro Camera\n| 2MP || 2MP || 2MP\n|-\n! Front Camera\n| 13MP || 13MP || 20MP\n|-\n!NFC\n|no\n|yes\n|yes\n|}\n! fingerprint sensor with ultra selfie mode.\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Android smartphones}}{{Xiaomi}}\n\n[[Category:Smartphones]]\n[[Category:Xiaomi]]\n[[Category:Mobile phones introduced in 2019]]\n", "text_old": "{{Short description|Redmi note series smartphone}}\n{{Infobox mobile phone|name=Xiaomi Redmi Note 8 Pro<br>Xiaomi Redmi Note 8\n|logo=\n| image = \n| codename =\n|manufacturer=[[Xiaomi]]\n|series=[[Xiaomi Redmi]]\n|released={{start date and age|df=yes|2019|08}}\n|predecessor=[[Redmi Note 7]]|successor=[[Redmi Note 9]]\n|type=[[Slate phone|Touchscreen]] [[smartphone]]\n|form=[[Slate phone|Slate]]\n|dimensions='''Redmi Note 8 Pro:'''<br/>H: 161.3 mm (6.35 in)<br/>W: 76.4 mm (3.01 in)<br/>D: 8.8 mm (0.35 in)<br/>\n'''Redmi Note 8:'''<br/>H: 158.3 mm (6.23 in)<br/>W: 75.3 mm (2.96 in)<br/>D: 8.4 mm (0.33 in)  \n|weight={{plainlist|\n*'''Redmi Note 8 Pro:'